  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": null,
    "text": "A few days later. You arrive at the clubroom early. Only Mawla is there."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": null,
    "text": "She's not writing. She's looking at the worm poster."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "Mawla",
    "text": "Hey."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "[player]",
    "text": "Hey."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": null,
    "text": "You sit. The room is quiet."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "Mawla",
    "text": "Can I tell you something?"
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "[player]",
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "Mawla",
    "text": "Before this club I didn't really write. I had thoughts but I didn't know what to do with them. They'd just sit there being too heavy."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "Mawla",
    "text": "Now I write them down and they're still heavy but they're — mine, in a different way. Contained. I can look at them."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "Mawla",
    "text": "That's what Vermia gave me. I don't tell her because she'd make it into a religious event. But."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "[player]",
    "text": "You should tell her anyway."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "Mawla",
    "text": "..."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "Mawla",
    "text": "Maybe."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": null,
    "text": "Another quiet. The worm poster stares. The clay figure on the windowsill has caught even more dust."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "Mawla",
    "text": "I'm glad you're in this club, [player]. It's different with you here. Better different."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "[player]",
    "text": "Same."
  },
  {
    "type": "line",
    "speaker": "Mawla",
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
